english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldStart}{code}{boldEnd} is your Roblox One-Time Code. Enter it into the login screen to log in. This code will expire in 15 minutes.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Do {boldStart}not{boldEnd} share this code. We will {boldStart}never{boldEnd} contact you to ask for it. If you did not request this code, there is no further action you need to take. If you receive numerous codes you did not request, we strongly encourage you to link a different email to your account(s) and {linkTagWithAuthenticatorHelpLinkStart}set up 2-Step Verification by Authenticator App{linkTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This login request was received from {geolocation}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank You,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Team

We noticed that the password changed for your Roblox account: {userName}. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, please click this link to undo the action:
{urlShown}

If you are happy with your new Roblox password, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up. Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page (https://www.roblox.com/help).

我們發現您變更了您的帳號 {userName} 的密碼。若您沒有要變更您的密碼，請按下此連結復原您的密碼：
{urlShown}

若您有變更密碼，您的變更已經生效，您不需要採取任何動作。請勿回覆此電子郵件。若您有任何問題，請前往 Roblox 協助頁面（https://www.roblox.com/help）。

description: Password Reset Email Body
english:
Dear {userName},

We noticed you have changed the password for your account. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, then we need you to contact customer service (https://www.roblox.com/support) to change the password back. That way we will know for sure that your account is secure and safe.

If you are happy with your new password on Roblox, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up.

Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page (https://www.roblox.com/help).
translation:
{userName} 您好，

我們發現您已變更您的密碼。若您沒有要變更您的密碼，或者認為有人不小心變更您的密碼，請聯絡客服人員（https://www.roblox.com/support）將密碼改回，確保帳號安全。

若您有變更密碼，您的變更已經生效，您不需要採取任何動作。

請勿回覆此訊息。若您有任何問題，請前往 Roblox 支援中心（https://www.roblox.com/help） 。

english: {paragraphStart}Your child is requesting to create the account {emphasisStart}{userName}{emphasisEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent's email address to create an account. In order for your child to complete the account creation process, you must consent to your child’s use of Roblox. You must enter the code below to complete the sign up flow and consent to your child’s use of Roblox. By entering the code, you and your child agree to the Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsLink}{hrefEnd}Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) You will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Verification Code: {code}{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide To Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our {aTagStartWithHref}{parentsLink}{hrefEnd}Parent’s Guide{aTagEnd} to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may remove your child's account anytime by contacting customer service at {aTagStartWithHref}{supportLink}{hrefEnd}https://www.roblox.com/support{aTagEnd}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPolicyLink}{hrefEnd}Privacy Policy{aTagEnd} for more information.{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您的小孩正在嘗試在 Roblox 建立帳號 {emphasisStart}{userName}{emphasisEnd}。Roblox 是一個線上娛樂平台，小孩在 Roblox 可以在使用者生成的沉浸式 3D 世界中共同想像、創作及玩樂。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您的小孩在建立帳號時向我們提供了使用者名稱、生日及家長的電子郵件地址。您必須同意小孩使用 Roblox，他才可以完成帳號建立流程。輸入下方驗證碼即可完成註冊流程並同意小孩使用 Roblox。輸入驗證碼及表示您和小孩同意 Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsLink}{hrefEnd}條款{aTagEnd}，包括仲裁條款。另外，您也會監督小孩的 Roblox 使用行為並對其全權負責。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}驗證碼：{code}{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Roblox 家長指南{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}我們推薦您閱讀{aTagStartWithHref}{parentsLink}{hrefEnd}家長指南{aTagEnd}讓您熟悉我們的平台，並學習為小孩營造正面的 Roblox 體驗的技巧。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}如果您要移除小孩的帳號，您可以在 {aTagStartWithHref}{supportLink}{hrefEnd}https://www.roblox.com/support{aTagEnd} 隨時聯絡客服人員。您的電子郵件地址不會用在其他用途、向第三方分享或與向小孩收集的其他個人資訊連結。若要了解更多資訊，請查看{aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPolicyLink}{hrefEnd}隱私權政策{aTagEnd}。{paragraphEnd}

description: Email body of verification email that is sent out when an under 13 user adds an email to the account
english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Your child created the account {boldTagStart}{username}{boldTagEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds. Our platform also provides a free development tool called “Roblox Studio” that allows users to create anything they imagine, from simple drag-and-drop building experiences to complex multiplayer games. Millions of kids have used Roblox to imagine what it’s like to create the ultimate theme park, compete as a professional race car driver, star in a fashion show, or simply build a dream home and hang out with friends.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This email is to inform you that your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent’s email address. The parent’s email address is only used for account management, password resets if the child forgets their password, and to notify parents of changes to the child’s account access. To verify your email address, please click the button below: {lineBreak}{lineBreak}{aTagStartWithHref}{verificationLink}{hrefEnd}{buttonStart}Verify Email{buttonEnd}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}About Roblox{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox is dedicated to building an enjoyable, family-friendly environment. translation: 您好，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}您的小孩已在 Roblox 建立帳號，使用者名稱為 {boldTagStart}{username}{boldTagEnd}。Roblox 是一個網路娛樂平台，玩家可以在我們眾多身歷其境的 3D 世界裡一起發揮想像力和同樂。玩家也可以使用我們免費的開發工具 Roblox Studio 創作簡單的模組和設計複雜的多人遊戲，盡情揮灑創意。已經有幾百萬名兒童透過 Roblox 實現他們的幻想，其中包括設計華麗的主題公園、以職業賽車手之姿和其他人競賽、成為時裝秀的焦點、化身超級英雄、邀請好友到夢寐以求的房子等等。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我們想讓您知道您的小孩已提供我們使用者名稱、出生日期和家長的電子郵件地址。家長的電子郵件地址只會用在帳號管理、密碼重置及通知帳號使用權限更改上。請按下此按鈕驗證您的電子郵件地址：{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{aTagStartWithHref}{verificationLink}{hrefEnd}{buttonStart}驗證電子郵件地址{buttonEnd}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}關於 Roblox{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 致力打造一個老少咸宜的愉快環境；我們持續地和數位安全專家增強我們的安全措施，確保所有玩家都能安心地同樂、聊天及合作。我們建議您閱讀以下的家長指南讓您更加熟悉我們的平台，並了解如何讓您的小孩的 Roblox 體驗更加豐富：{aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 也備有{boldTagStart}家長監護功能{boldTagEnd}。家長可以啟用家長 PIN 碼，變更小孩的通訊與聊天設定。若要尋找這些監護功能，您可於登入小孩的帳號，並前往帳號設定中的安全性及隱私權標籤。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}若要新增家長 PIN 碼，請前往：{aTagStartWithHref}{accountSecurityLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSecurityLink}{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}若要變更聊天設定，請前往： {aTagStartWithHref}{accountPrivacyLink}{hrefEnd}{accountPrivacyLink}{aTagEnd}。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}隱私權{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}若要移除您的小孩的帳號，您可以前往此處聯絡客服人員：{aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}。您的電子郵件地址不會用在其他用途、向第三方揭露或與您的小孩的個人資料合併。若您需要更多資訊，您可以前往此連結查看我們的隱私權政策：{aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}謝謝您，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 團隊 {lineBreak}{lineBreak} 請勿直接回覆此電子郵件。{lineBreak}{lineBreak} {aTagStartWithHref}{robloxWebsiteLink}{hrefEnd}{robloxWebsiteLink}{aTagEnd} {lineBreak}{lineBreak} {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}

english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Your child created the account {username} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and explore together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds. Our platform also provides a free development tool called “Roblox Studio” that allows users to create anything they imagine, from simple drag-and-drop building experiences to complex multiplayer games. Millions of kids have used Roblox to imagine what it’s like to create the ultimate theme park, compete as a professional race car driver, star in a fashion show, or simply build a dream home and hang out with friends.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This email is to inform you that your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent’s email address. The parent’s email address is only used for account management, password resets if the child forgets their password, and to notify parents of changes to the child’s account access. To verify your email address, please click the button below:{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{verificationLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}About Roblox{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox is dedicated to building an enjoyable, family-friendly environment. We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: {parentalPageLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox also offers parental controls. Parents can enable a parent PIN and change their child’s communication and chat settings. You can find these controls by visiting the security and privacy tabs in the account settings while logged into your child’s account.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}To add a parent PIN, please visit: {accountSecurityLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}To change chat settings, please visit: {chatPrivacyLink} {lineBreak}{lineBreak}Privacy{lineBreak}{lineBreak} You may remove your child's account by contacting customer service at {supportPageLink}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our privacy policy for more information at {privacyPageLink}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Team{lineBreak}Do not reply to this email directly.{lineBreak}{robloxWebiteLink}{lineBreak}{supportPageLink}

Dear {username},

If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, then we need you to contact customer service (https://www.roblox.com/support) to change the email back. That way we will know for sure that your account is secure and safe.

If you are happy with your new email address on Roblox you don't have to do anything! It's already set up.
Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions please email {robloxInfoEmailAddress}.
translation:
{username} 您好，

我們發現您已電子郵件地址從 {oldEmailAddress} 變更為 {newEmailAddress}。若您沒有要變更您的電子郵件地址，或者認為有人不小心變更您的電子郵件地址，請聯絡客服人員（https://www.roblox.com/support）將電子郵件地址改回，確保您的帳號的安全。

若您有變更電子郵件地址，您的變更已經生效，您不需要採取任何動作。
請勿回覆此訊息。若您有任何問題，請聯絡 {robloxInfoEmailAddress} 。

english: I am invited to a private server
translation: 有人邀請我加入私人伺服器

english: Who can invite me to private servers?

description: Subject for email verification email, which is used to let the user confirm that their email address is associated with this roblox account.
Body text for email verification email. This comes before a button that the user can click to proceed with confirming that they want to associate this email to the given Roblox account.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thanks for choosing to secure your Roblox account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} by providing an email address.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}If you submitted this request, please click the button below to complete the verification process:{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好，{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}謝謝您提供電子郵件地址保護您的 Roblox 帳號 {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}若您有進行此請求，請按下以下按鈕完成驗證程序：{paragraphEnd}

description: Text on a button in the email verification email. Clicking this button lets the user confirm that they want this email address to be associated with their Roblox account for security purposes.
Second part of the body of the email verification email. This comes after the 'verify email' button.
Footer displayed at the bottom of the 'email verification' email.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there has been an attempt to verify a Roblox account with your email. If you did not make this request, please disregard this email.
translation: 請勿直接回覆此電子郵件。您因為有人嘗試使用您的電子郵件地址驗證 Roblox 帳號而收到此電子郵件。若您沒有進行驗證請求，請忽略此電子郵件。

description: Informative links at the bottom of the 'email verification' email.
Subject line for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is sent to the parent of the user, who is responsible for taking action on authorizing the email.

First part of the body text for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is directed at the parent of the user. Below this text is an "I Agree, Verify Email" button that the parent can click to proceed.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child created the account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent's email address. Please confirm this email address is correct by {emphasisStart}clicking the button below to complete the validation process{emphasisEnd}. Regardless of whether you validate the parental email address or not, the child will still be able to retain their account and chat with others.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}By clicking the "I Agree, Validate Email" button you also agree that (a) You and your child agree to the Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) You will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好，{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您的小孩 {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} 在 Roblox 註冊了帳號。Roblox 是一個讓兒童在使用者創作的沉浸式 3D 世界裡一起想像、創作和玩樂的網路娛樂平台。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您的小孩給我們提供了使用者名稱、出生日期及家長的電子郵件地址。為了確認電子郵件地址正確，請{emphasisStart}點擊以下按鈕完成驗證程序{emphasisEnd}。無論您有沒有驗證家長的電子郵件地址，您的小孩仍然可以使用他的帳號和其他人聊天。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}按下「我同意，驗證電子郵件地址」即表示您同意（一）您和小孩同意 Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}條款{aTagEnd}和仲裁條款，以及（二）您會監督小孩的 Roblox 使用行為並單獨為其負責。{paragraphEnd}

description: Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('by clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent.
translation: 我同意，驗證電子郵件地址

description: Second part of the body text in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is shown after a button that the parent can click to proceed with email verification. 'Parent's Guide to Roblox' and 'Privacy' are paragraph headers.
english: {paragraphStart}You can set your child's safety and parental control settings for their Roblox account at {aTagStartWithHref}{accountSettingsLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSettingsLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide to Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: {aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may remove your child's account anytime by contacting customer service at {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our privacy policy for more information at {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您可以在 {aTagStartWithHref}{accountSettingsLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSettingsLink}{aTagEnd} 修改小孩的安全與家長監護設定。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Roblox 家長指南{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}我們建議您閱讀家長指南， 讓您可以更加了解我們的平台，以及學習如何為小孩營造正面的 Roblox 體驗：{aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}隱私{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您可以隨時在 {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd} 請求客服人員移除小孩的帳號。您的電子郵件地址將不會用在其他用途上、洩漏給第三方組織或與其他小孩提供的其他個人資訊合併。若要了解更多資訊，請在 {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd} 閱讀我們的隱私權政策。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}謝謝您，{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Roblox 團隊{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer at the bottom of the 'email verification' email for users under 13.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there has been an attempt to verify a Roblox account with your email. If you did not make this request, please disregard this email.
translation: 請勿直接回覆此電子郵件。您因為有人嘗試使用您的電子郵件地址驗證 Roblox 帳號而收到此電子郵件。若您沒有進行驗證請求，請忽略此電子郵件。

description: Links at the bottom of the 'email verification' email for users under 13.

english: When this setting is enabled, the PIN must be provided before changing settings.
translation: 當此設定啟用時，您變更設定之前都必須輸入 PIN 碼。

english: When this setting is enabled, this account can only access content that is appropriate for all audiences. Additionally, Communication Settings (under the {linkStart}Privacy{linkEnd} page) will be set to Off.
translation: 當此設定啟用時，此帳號將只能存取適合所有年齡層的內容。另外，位於{linkStart}隱私{linkEnd}頁面的通訊設定將設為關閉。

english: Parental Controls allow parents to choose the correct settings that will control what experiences their child can access.
translation: 家長可以使用家長監護裡的設定控制小孩可以進入的體驗。

english: This setting controls what type of experiences this user is allowed to visit.
translation: 此設定控制此使用者可以參訪的體驗類型。

english: Communication Settings are locked because Account Restrictions (under {linkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} page) are enabled
translation: 因帳號限制（在{linkStart}家長監護{linkEnd}頁面下）啟用中，通訊設定已鎖定。

description: DO NOT TRANSLATE, CAN BE DELETED

translation: 家長 PIN 碼已啟用
家長 PIN 碼已停用

description: Label next to toggle for enabling email-based two step verification.
Label next to toggle for enabling authenticator-based two step verification.
Requirement for enabling authenticator-based two step verification.
Displayed as help text when authenticator-based two step verification is already enabled.
english: Download an app on your phone to generate unique security codes. Suggested apps include Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator, and Twilio's Authy.
translation: 在手機上下載能生成唯一安全碼的 App。我們建議使用 Google Authenticator、Microsoft Authenticator、Twilio Authy 等 App。

english: Scan the QR code above into your authenticator app, then enter the generated code below.
translation: 將上方的 QR 碼掃入驗證器 App，並在下方輸入生成的驗證碼。

english: Enter the manual entry key above into your authenticator app, then enter the generated code below.
translation: 將上方的手動輸入碼輸入到驗證器 App，並在下方輸入生成的驗證碼。

description: Message to user for manual Authenticator code entry.
english: Can't scan the QR code? Click here for manual entry.
translation: 無法掃描 QR 碼？按下此處取得手動輸入碼。

english: QR code has expired. Please close the modal and try again.
translation: QR 碼已過期，請關閉視窗再重新嘗試。

description: The title of the dialog that asks you to input your password before generating recovery codes.
The title of the dialog displaying the newly generated recovery codes.
The description text on the dialog prompting the user to generate new recovery codes by providing their password.
english: Please enter your account password to generate new backup codes.
translation: 若要生成新的備用碼，請輸入您的帳號的密碼。

english: These are your new backup codes. Please save them as you will not be able to see the codes again later.
translation: 這是您的新備用碼。復原碼只會為您顯示一次，請妥善保管。

description: Check box confirming the user has saved their recovery codes.
A label on the modal for generating new recovery codes  giving notice that the number of remaining unused recovery codes will no longer work.
english: {activeCodeCount} backup codes will become invalid when new ones are generated.
translation: {activeCodeCount} 個備用碼將在新的復原碼生成時失效。

description: Label next to button for generating two step verification recovery codes.
Help text on the two step verification recovery codes section card.
english: Generate and use backup codes in case you lose access to your 2-Step Verification option. Do not share your backup codes with anyone.
translation: 無法使用雙步驟驗證時即可生成和使用備用碼。請勿與他人分享備用碼。

english: You need {robuxIcon} {robuxToBuy} more to change your username. Would you like to buy more Robux?
translation: 您還需要 {robuxIcon} {robuxToBuy} 才能變更使用者名稱。您要加購 Robux 嗎？

english: To keep you and the community safe, age verification is required to access certain features on Roblox.
translation: 為了確保您和我們社群的安全，只有通過年齡驗證的帳號才可以使用部分 Roblox 功能。

description: Label next to toggle after enabling email-based two step verification.
english: Your Account is Protected via Email Verification
translation: 您的帳號已受到電子郵件驗證保護

description: Label next to button for generating two step verification recovery codes after two step verification recovery codes have already been generated.
Message to user that appears after the user has generated recovery codes.
translation: 您有 {activeCodeCount} 個未使用的備用碼。

description: Virtual transaction 2SV
english: 2-step Verification is required to make further transactions.
translation: 若要繼續交易，請完成雙步驟驗證。

english: If you change your birthday, your age will no longer be verified.
translation: 若您變更生日，您將會失去年齡驗證。

description: prompt to add screentime restrictions for children in parental controls
english: You can add restriction hours to your child's account.
translation: 您可以為小孩的帳號新增限制時間。

description: prompt for selecting restriction hours time. ex. "Blocked From 6:00 AM"
prompt for selecting restriction hours time. ex. "Blocked Until 9:00 AM"
prompt for selecting restriction days. ex. "Repeat every Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday"

english: Your time zone has been updated successfully!

description: button for adding screentime restrictions
error shown when user sets screentime restrictions that allow less than 1 hour of playtime
english: People must have at least one hour of allowed time.
translation: 帳號須至少有一小時的自由時間。

description: error shown if user inputs a screentime restriction with invalid times (ex 4pm to 10am)
english: Blocked Until time must be later than the Blocked From time.
translation: 限制結束時間必須晚於限制開始時間。

description: prompts a user to update their time zone when stored time zone doesn't match current device timezone
english: Looks like you are in the time zone: {timeZone}, update time zone?
translation: 系統判斷您目前的時區為 {timeZone}，更新時區？

description: prompts user to save screentime restriction settings
english: Click on Save to update your changes.
translation: 按下儲存即可套用更新。

description: ex. Every Wednesday, Monday, Tuesday. Should include the space after "every" (if this is relevant in translated language)
heading for section where parents can add restrictions to when their children can play Roblox

english: You must select at least one day of the week.
translation: 須至少選擇一星期中的一天。

description: tooltip text for korea screentime controls
english: The Youth Protection Revision Act, commonly known as the Shutdown Law or Cinderella Law, is an act of the South Korean National Assembly which forbids children under the age of 16 to play online video games between the hours of 00:00 and 06:00.
translation: 南韓國會制定的青少年保護修訂條例禁止 16 歲以下兒童在午夜 12:00 到上午 6:00 之間進入線上遊戲。

description: tooltip label for korea screentime curfew law
english: 12am - 6am is automatically restricted and cannot be edited.
translation: 午夜 12 點到上午 6:00 為自動限制時間，無法編輯。

description: robux spend friction
english: Improve your account security. A code will be required for some actions like logging in.
translation: 加強帳號安全。您登入或進行部分操作時將需要驗證碼。

english: Your username change request has been processed. Your username was changed from {oldUsername} to {newUsername}. If you did not request a username change, please review our account help information at our {startLink}Help Center{endLink}. Please do not reply to directly to this email as replies to this email address are not received.
translation: Roblox 使用者您好，您的使用者名稱變更請求已處理完畢，您的使用者名稱已從 {oldUsername} 變更為 {newUsername}。若您沒有請求變更使用者名稱，請前往 {startLink}Roblox 支援中心{endLink}查看帳號協助資訊。請勿直接回覆此電子郵件，我們無法在此電子郵件地址接收訊息。

description: Make sure that user wants to disable email two step verification when another two step verification method exists.
english: If you turn off 2-Step Verification with Email, a security code from your email will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. Are you sure?
translation: 若關閉電子郵件雙步驟驗證，您登入或進行部分操作時將不再需要輸入電子郵件內的驗證碼。確定？

description: Make sure that user wants to disable authenticator two step verification when another two step verification method exists.
english: If you turn off 2-Step Verification with Authenticator, a security code from the Authenticator App will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. Are you sure?
translation: 若關閉電子郵件雙步驟驗證，您登入或進行部分操作時將不再需要輸入電子郵件內的驗證碼。確定？

english: You must be at least 18 years old to save screen time restrictions.
translation: 您必須 18 歲以上才可儲存使用時間限制。

english: Enabling voice chat will use your microphone input in voice enabled experiences.
translation: 啟用語音聊天時，支援語音聊天的體驗將會使用您的麥克風輸入。

english: By clicking 'Verify My Age' you will be completing an ID verification process operated by our third party service provider.
translation: 按下「驗證我的年齡」後，您將會開始由第三方服務供應商執行的身分驗證程序。

english: Use a physical key, your device's face ID, or touch ID to validate your identity.
translation: 使用實體金鑰、裝置的 FaceID 或裝置的 TouchID 驗證身分。

english: Supported on web browsers, iPhone, and iPad. A hardware security key or device’s biometrics like fingerprint or facial recognition.
translation: 支援網路瀏覽器、iPhone 及 iPad。硬體安全金鑰或指紋、臉部辨識等裝置生物辨識功能。

description: First part of the body text for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is directed at the parent of the user. Below this text is an "I Agree, Validate Email" button that the parent can click to proceed.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}This email is being sent to give you notice about your child’s account on Roblox, {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}, and the option to validate your email address to enable added security and parental controls for your child’s account.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}When your child first created an account on Roblox, we collected the following information: username, password, birthdate, and gender. You or your child recently added a parent email address to the account. Please confirm that this email address is correct by {emphasisStart}clicking the button below:{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好，{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}我們傳送此封電子郵件是為了通知您關於您子女在 Roblox 上帳戶的事宜{emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}，並告知您可驗證您的電子郵件地址來為您子女的帳戶啟用額外的安全性和家長監護功能。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您的子女在 Roblox 上首次建立帳戶時，我們收集了以下資訊：使用者名稱、密碼、出生日期和性別。您或您的子女最近為該帳戶新增了家長的電子郵件地址。如您確認這是正確的電子郵件地址，請{emphasisStart}按一下下方的按鈕：{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description:
Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('By clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent with 
Description.VerificationEmail.Body.Under13.V4.
english: {paragraphStart}By validating your email address, you will have the ability to reset your child’s password (when necessary), get updates on your child’s account activities, and set your child's safety and parental control settings for their Roblox account at https://www.roblox.com/my/account#!.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}If you do not validate your email address, your child will still be able to use their account, play on Roblox and access most features, including filtered text chat.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your email address will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Apart from a parent’s email, we do not otherwise collect, use, or disclose personal information from child users.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Please review our privacy policy for more information at https://www.roblox.com/info/privacy.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide to Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Roblox is an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: https://www.roblox.com/info/parents{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Other Important Information{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may refuse to allow your child’s participation on Roblox, request that we delete your child's account, and/or request that we delete your email address at any time. To take any of these actions, please contact customer service at https://www.roblox.com/support.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}By allowing your child to maintain an account on Roblox, you agree that (a) you and your child agree to the {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) you will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}The Roblox Team{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}驗證您的電子郵件地址後，您將能夠（在必要時）重設子女帳戶的密碼、獲得子女帳戶活動的最新消息，並在 https://www.roblox.com/my/account#! 為其 Roblox 帳戶設定安全性和家長監護功能。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}如果您未驗證您的電子郵件地址，您的子女仍可使用其帳戶、在 Roblox 上遊玩並存取大多數功能，包括經過過濾的文字聊天。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您的電子郵件地址不會用於其他任何目的、不會透露給第三方，也不會與任何從您子女帳戶收集的其他個人資訊結合。除了家長的電子郵件之外，我們不會以其他方式收集、使用或透露自兒童使用者端取得的個人資訊。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您可以前往 https://www.roblox.com/info/privacy 查看我們的隱私權政策以了解更多資訊。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Roblox 家長指南{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Roblox 是一個可讓兒童在由使用者創作的沉浸式 3D 世界裡發揮想像力、盡情創作和玩樂的線上娛樂平台。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}建議您可以閱讀我們的家長指南，以更加了解我們的平台，並能得到一些實用的技巧，可幫助您的孩子在 Roblox 上創造良好體驗：https://www.roblox.com/info/parents{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}其他重要事項{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您隨時可以拒絕讓您的小孩使用 Roblox、要求我們刪除您子女的帳戶和/或要求我們刪除您的電子郵件地址。如要採取以上任何操作，請透過 https://www.roblox.com/support 聯絡客戶服務團隊。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}如果您允許子女保留其在 Roblox 上的帳戶，即表示您同意 (a) 您和您的子女皆同意 {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox 的條款{aTagEnd}，包括仲裁條款，並且 (b) 您會監督子女使用 Roblox 的情形，並為其行為負完全責任。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}謝謝您，{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Roblox 團隊{paragraphEnd}

description: Developer exchange welcome page heading
english: Welcome to the Roblox Developer Exchange!
translation: 歡迎來到 Roblox Developer Exchange！

english: The Developer Exchange Program (also known as DevEx) allows you to earn money by creating awesome experiences on Roblox.
translation: Developer Exchange 企劃（又稱 DevEx）可以讓您透過在 Roblox 創作優質的體驗賺錢。

english: Once you earn {minCashoutValue} Robux or more, you are eligible to convert your virtual earnings to real-world cash.
translation: 您賺得 {minCashoutValue} Robux 以上時即擁有資格將虛擬貨幣轉換成真實金錢。

english: To use DevEx, you must agree to DevEx Terms of Service and meet the simple requirements set out in those Terms, some of which are as follows:
translation: 若要使用 DevEx，您必須同意 DevEx 服務條款並遵守其基本需求，其中包括：

english: Minimum of {minCashoutValue} earned Robux in your account;

translation: 擁有已驗證的電子郵件地址、
擁有{startVerifyEmailLink}已驗證{endVerifyEmailLink}的電子郵件地址
有效的 DevEx 平台帳號、

english: 13 years of age or older; and
Community member in good standing, having complied with {termLinkStart}Roblox's Terms of Use{termLinkEnd}.
translation: 持續遵守 {termLinkStart}Roblox 使用條款{termLinkEnd}，紀錄良好的社群成員。

english: You may initiate a request to exchange Robux for cash through the Developer Exchange once each calendar month.Requests are usually processed within 2 - 4 weeks. DevEx conversions are calculated in US Dollars.
translation: 您單月可以透過 Developer Exchange 進行一次將 Robux 兌現的請求，請求通常會在 2 到 4 個星期內處理完畢。DevEx 兌換率以美元計算。

english: When you meet all the requirements, you will see a "Cash Out" button on this page. Click it and follow the instructions to get your payment started.
translation: 您符合所有需求時將會在此頁面看到「兌現」按鈕，點擊之後依照指示即可開始付款作業。

english: We recommend that you familiarize yourself with the tax treatment of DevEx payments and the fees associated with different payment methods on DevEx transactions before you cash out.
translation: 在兌現之前，我們建議您先了解 DevEx 付款的課稅方式和不同 DevEx 交易付款模式的相關費用。

english: If your request is approved, and if this is your first time cashing out, you will receive an email inviting you to create an account on our DevEx portal. You will be prompted to enter your information at account creation.
translation: 若您是第一次兌現，您將會在請求被批准後收到一封邀請您在 DevEx 平台建立帳號的電子郵件。您在建立帳號時將會被要求輸入資訊。

english: Please make sure your information is entered accurately into the DevEx portal, and is kept up to date at all times.
translation: 請確保在 DevEx 平台輸入的資訊正確無誤，並持續將其更新。

english: The information you provide is used to ensure all payments comply with laws and regulations.  Inaccuracies in information provided could impact your payment.
translation: 您提供的資訊將會用來確保所有付款皆符合相關法規。當提供的資訊有誤時，您的付款可能會受到影響。

english: Your Developer Exchange request has been processed
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求已處理完畢

english: Your Developer Exchange request has been rejected
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求已遭拒

english: We have processed your request to our Developer Exchange; you should receive funds in your account shortly.
translation: 我們已處理您的開發者兌換請求，資金稍後應會進入您的帳號。

english: If you have any questions about this transaction, please write in at
translation: 如果您對此筆交易有問題，請聯絡：

english: Please visit the DevEx FAQ for more information regarding your Declined request. If you have any questions, please write in at
translation: 請前往 DevEx FAQ 了解更多關於請求遭拒的資訊。如果您有任何問題，請聯絡：

english: Thank you for participating in the DevEx program!
translation: 謝謝您參與 DevEx 企劃！

translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：不符合資格。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Invalid PayPal information. The PayPal information you provided was invalid and the payment wasn't able to be processed and your DevEx request was declined. Please update your PayPal information for your next DevEx request.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：無效 PayPal 資訊。您提供的 PayPal 資訊無效，無法處理付款，DevEx 請求因而遭拒。請在送出下一次 DevEx 請求時更新您的 PayPal 資訊。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: User Request.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：使用者請求。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Failed to submit Tax Form. Please submit a valid Tax Form to the DevEx Portal.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：無法提交稅單。請向 DevEx 平台提交有效稅單。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Technical Issue. We are looking into resolving the issue.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：技術問題。我們正在研究和處理問題。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: DevEx Portal Registration Incomplete. Please reference the DevEx FAQ for information about the DevEx Portal.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：未完成 DevEx 平台註冊。請閱讀 DevEx FAQ 了解關於 DevEx 平台的資訊。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Insufficient Earned Robux.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：賺得 Robux 不足。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Insufficient Funds. Your earnings aren't valid for DevEx and we are unable to accept your DevEx request at the amount you have submitted.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：資金不足。您的收入不是 DevEx 有效收入，我們無法依您申請的金額接受您的 DevEx 請求。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Unable to Review Game Associated to Earnings. We were unable to confirm the eligibility of your game because we weren't able to review the games(s) associated to your earnings.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：無法審核與收入相關的遊戲。因為我們無法審核與您的收入相關的遊戲，我們無法確認您的遊戲的資格。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Account Ownership Concern.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：帳號所有權疑慮。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Name Discrepancy. We noticed that the name of your current DevEx request differs from the initial DevEx request and/or name listed on your DevEx Portal.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：名稱不符。我們注意到目前 DevEx 請求的名稱與初始 DevEx 請求和（或）DevEx 平台的名稱不符。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Submit DevEx with full legal name.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：請使用法定姓名提交 DevEx 請求。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: ID Verification Incomplete.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：未完成 ID 驗證。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: ID Verification Incomplete.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：未完成 ID 驗證。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Email Provided on Devex Request is Already in Use. We are unable to send you a DevEx portal invitation to the email listed on your DevEx request because it is already in use.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：DevEx 請求上的電子郵件地址使用中。DevEx 請求上的電子郵件地址使用中，因此我們無法向其傳送 DevEx 平台邀請。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Certificate of Non-US Activities Incomplete. We noticed that you did not complete the Certificate of No US activities in the Tax Form section on the DevEx portal.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：未完成美國外活動認證。我們發現您尚未完成 DevEx 平台稅單區塊的美國外活動認證。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Failed to submit Payment Method. A Payment Method must be submitted in order to approve your DevEx Request.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：無法提交付款方式。必須提交付款方式才可批准 DevEx 請求。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Required DevEx portal documents not submitted.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：未繳交必要的 DevEx 平台文件。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: DevEx portal is blocked. Your DevEx portal account is locked for a compliance issue.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：DevEx 平台遭到鎖定。因法律遵循關係，您的 DevEx 平台帳號已遭到鎖定。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Above maximum payment method threshold. We cannot process your current DevEx request because our vendor's provider has a maximum payment threshold. Your current DevEx request has been rejected for this reason.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：大於付款方式上限。無法處理您目前的 DevEx 請求，因為我們的合作廠商的供應商有付款上限。您目前的 DevEx 請求因此遭拒。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Below minimum payment method threshold. We cannot process your current DevEx request because our vendor's provider has a minimum payment threshold. Your current DevEx request has been rejected for this reason.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：小於付款方式下限。無法處理您目前的 DevEx 請求，因為我們的合作廠商的供應商有付款下限。您目前的 DevEx 請求因此遭拒。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: Failed to complete Tipalti registration. Please reference the DevEx FAQ for information about the DevEx Portal.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求無法處理的原因為：未完成 Tipalti 註冊。請閱讀 DevEx FAQ 了解關於 DevEx 平台的資訊。

english: Your Developer Exchange request was unable to be processed for the following reason: DevEx Payment Rejected. We could not process your DevEx payment at this time due to incorrect banking information entered. Please login to your DevEx portal to verify that your banking information is correct.
translation: 您的開發者兌換請求因下列原因無法處理：DevEx 付款遭拒。因為銀行資訊有誤，我們目前無法處理您的 DevEx 付款。請登入 DevEx 平台確認銀行資訊正確。

The other {robloxFeePercent}% will go to Roblox and other users including the item creator.
translation: 所有市集交易的收入（包括轉賣收入）將會由 Roblox 和與交易相關的使用者共享。以轉賣為例，使用者接受您的價格時，您（轉賣者）將會獲得他付的 Robux 金額的 {yourSharePercent}%。Roblox 和其他使用者（包括道具創作者）將會獲得剩下的 {robloxFeePercent}%。

english: No news about your best friends... want to know what your best friends are up to?
translation: 沒有您的好友的消息……想知道您的好友在做什麼嗎？

english: Nearly all Roblox experiences are built by people like you. Here are some of our favorites:
translation: Roblox 體驗幾乎都是由像您一樣的人創作。以下是幾個我們最愛的體驗：

translation: 從{linkStart}型錄{linkEnd}取得新衣物，自訂您的虛擬人偶。

english: No matter what you're looking for, if it's Roblox related, there are people talking about it {linkStart}here{linkEnd}.

first paragraph under what's Roblox heading on landing page
english: Roblox helps power the imagination of people around the world. As the largest growing social experience platform, over 44 million people come to Roblox every month to create adventures, play games, roleplay, and learn with friends. We call it the ‘Imagination Platform’.
translation: Roblox 可以激發全世界的人的想像力。作為最龐大且持續成長的社交體驗平台，每個月有超過 4400 萬人在 Roblox 一起創作、遊樂、扮演及學習，我們稱之為「想像力平台」。

description: second paragraph under what's Roblox on the landing page
english: Roblox is the best place to Imagine with Friends. With the largest online user-generated experience platform, and over 15 million experiences created by users, Roblox is the #1 site for kids and teens (comScore). Every day, virtual explorers come to Roblox to create adventures, play games, role play, and learn with their friends in a family-friendly, immersive, 3D environment.
translation: Roblox 是與朋友發揮想像力的最佳場所。做為最大的使用者創作線上體驗平台，Roblox 擁有超過 1500 萬款全由使用者創作的體驗，這也使得美國公司 comScore 認證 Roblox 為兒童及青少年網站的首選。每天都有虛擬探險家前往 Roblox 老少咸宜、身歷其境的 3D 環境一起創作、遊樂、扮演及學習。

You can find more information in your parental preferences associated with playtime and transactions.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox is a game that has many mini experiences in different genres such as role playing, sports, action, and many more.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox pricing policy is a freemium model with in-game purchases.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{htmlContentRatingLogoImages}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}The Roblox Team{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Please do not reply to this message as it will not be delivered to the originator.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{htmlBoldOpen}{htmlAHrefAccountSafetyPage}Account Safety{htmlCloseAHref}{htmlBoldClose} | {htmlBoldOpen}{htmlAhrefSupportPage}Support{htmlCloseAHref}{htmlBoldClose}

english: Roblox Premium is a {durationType} subscription that costs {costPrice}. Payment will be charged to the iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Roblox Premium will automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged {renewalPrice} for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings.
translation: Roblox Premium 是{durationType}費用 {costPrice} 的訂閱制度。完成購買時，我們會向您的 iTunes 帳號收費。Roblox Premium 會自動續訂，但若您目前的訂閱還剩超過 24 小時，您可以關閉自動更新。在您的訂閱結束的前 24 小時以內，我們將會向您的帳號收取 {renewalPrice}。您可以在帳號設定頁面管理訂閱與自動更新選項。

english: Roblox Premium is a monthly subscription that costs {costPrice}. Payment will be charged to the iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Roblox Premium will automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged {renewalPrice} for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings. If you're under 18 make sure you have the permission of your parent or legal guardian before making a purchase. Making a purchase without permission may result in your account being deleted.
translation: Roblox Premium 是每個月費用 {costPrice} 的訂閱制度。完成購買時，我們會向您的 iTunes 帳號收費。Roblox Premium 會自動續訂，但若您目前的訂閱還剩超過 24 小時，您可以關閉自動更新。在您的訂閱結束的前 24 小時以內，我們將會向您的帳號收取 {renewalPrice}。您可以在帳號設定頁面管理訂閱與自動更新選項。若您未滿 18 歲，請在購買之前徵求家長或法定監護人的同意。若您在未經同意下進行購買，您的帳號可能會遭刪除。

english: Buy Robux to purchase upgrades for your avatar or special abilities in experiences.{lineBreak} Subscribe to Roblox Premium and get even more Robux each month, as well as bonus features. Premium is billed every month until cancelled. {learnMoreLinkStart}Learn more here.{learnMoreLinkEnd}
translation: Robux 可以用來購買虛擬人偶強化或體驗內的特殊能力。{lineBreak}訂閱 Roblox Premium 可以每一個月獲得更多 Robux，並使用額外功能。Roblox Premium 採月費制，直到取消為止。{learnMoreLinkStart}前往此處了解更多{learnMoreLinkEnd}。

english: When you buy Robux you receive only a limited, non-refundable, non-transferable, revocable license to use Robux, which has no value in real currency. By selecting the Premium subscription package, (1) you agree that you are over 18 and that you authorize us to charge your account every month until you cancel the subscription, and (2) you represent that you understand and agree to the Terms of Use, which includes an agreement to arbitrate any dispute between you and Roblox, and {privacyLinkStart}Privacy Policy{privacyLinkEnd}. You can cancel at any time by clicking “Cancel subscription” on the {billingLinkStart}billing tab{billingLinkEnd} of the setting page. If you cancel, you will still be charged for the current billing period. See {termsLinkStart}Terms of Use{termsLinkEnd} for other limitations.
translation: 您購買 Robux 時只會獲得使用 Robux 的授權。該授權具有限制性、無法退款、無法轉讓、可被收回，並且沒有金錢價值。您選擇 Premium 訂閱即代表 (1) 您年滿 18 歲，允許我們在您取消訂閱之前每個月向您的帳號收費，及 (2) 您了解並同意使用條款（其中包括透過調解處理您與 Roblox 的爭議的協議）和{privacyLinkStart}隱私權政策{privacyLinkEnd}。您隨時可以前往設定頁面裡的{billingLinkStart}帳務標籤{billingLinkEnd}使用「取消訂閱」按鈕取消您的會員資格。若您取消，您依然需要為目前的帳單週期付費。若要獲得其他限制相關的資訊，請查看{termsLinkStart}使用條款{termsLinkEnd}。

translation: 對不起，您已到達購買上限，無法完成交易。請在 24 到 72 小時候重新嘗試交易。若仍然無法完成交易，您最長可能要到 30 天候才可以進行新的購買。購買上限無法變更或移除。

english: ERROR: PayPal transaction has been declined.
translation: 錯誤：PayPal 交易遭到拒絕。

english: ERROR: Transaction was declined by payment provider.
translation: 錯誤：交易遭到付款服務商家拒絕。

english: Duplicate transaction detected from the payment provider. Purchase did not go through. Please try again in a few minutes. Do not refresh the payment web page.
translation: 偵測到來自付款服務商家的重複交易，購買未完成。請幾分鐘後重新嘗試，請勿重新整理付款頁面。

english: ERROR: PayPal transaction has been blocked.
translation: 錯誤：PayPal 交易遭到阻擋。

english: An unexpected error has occurred. Please try again in a few minutes.
translation: 發生意外錯誤，請幾分鐘後重新嘗試。

english: This card number is not valid. Please check number and try again.
translation: 此卡號無效，請檢查卡號再重新嘗試。

english: This card number has too few digits. Please check number and try again.
translation: 此卡號數元不足，請檢查卡號再重新嘗試。

english: This card number has too many digits. Please check number and try again.
translation: 此卡號數元過多，請檢查卡號再重新嘗試。

english: The card entry included non-numeric characters. Please check number and try again.
translation: 卡號含有數元以外的字元，請檢查卡號再重新嘗試。

english: We have experienced an error in processing your payment. Please try again.
translation: 處理付款時發生問題，請重新嘗試。

english: This security code is invalid. Please check number and try again.
translation: 此安全碼無效，請檢查安全碼再重新嘗試。

english: This security code has too few digits. Please check number and try again.
translation: 此安全碼數元不足，請檢查安全碼再重新嘗試。

english: This security code has too many digits. Please check number and try again.
translation: 此安全碼數元過多，請檢查安全碼再重新嘗試。

english: There was an error in processing your payment. Please try again.
translation: 處理付款時發生問題，請重新嘗試。

english: Payment has failed. Please try again.
An unexpected error has occurred with your payment.
By selecting a payment type, I agree that I am the parent or legal guardian of the account owner and I authorize this purchase.
translation: 選擇付款方式即代表我是帳號所有人的家長或法定監護人，並同意此項買賣。

english: You must be the parent or legal guardian of the account owner to make this purchase. Card owners may be contacted for confirmation.
translation: 您必須是帳號所有人的家長或法定監護人才能進行此項買賣。我們可能會聯絡金融卡持有人進行確認。

english: Using a card without permission will result in the account being deleted.
translation: 若您未經許可使用金融卡，您的帳號將會遭到刪除。

english: Your transaction cannot be completed at this time, as you have reached a transaction limit. Please visit our {startLink}Help Center{endLink} for general information on purchasing. Please note Customer Support cannot change or remove these limits.
translation: 您已達到交易上限，目前無法完成您的交易。若要了解更多關於買賣的基本資訊，請前往{startLink}支援中心{endLink}。請注意，客服人員無法變更或解除交易上限。

english: An unexpected error occurred. It may take up to 5 minutes for your transaction to process. Please check the My Transactions page to see if it processed successfully.
translation: 發生意外錯誤。交易可能需要 5 分鐘完成。請在我的交易頁面查看交易是否已成功處理。

english: An error occurred and payment was unsuccessful. Please try again.
translation: 發生錯誤，未完成付款。請重新嘗試。

english: There was an error connecting to PayPal. Please try again.
translation: 連線到 PayPal 時發生問題，請重新嘗試。

english: Something went wrong, please refresh and try again.
translation: 發生錯誤，請重新整理並再試一次。

english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}We're reaching out to you to let you know that the following content has been removed from Roblox: {AudioUrlLink}. This content has been removed under Roblox’s intellectual property policies and you have received a refund for the cost of the audio upload.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox respects the intellectual property rights of others and requires that all members of the Roblox community do the same. You should make sure you have the legal right (such as permission from the copyright owner) to upload content you haven’t created yourself. You should remove from your account, including within your experiences, content that belongs to others that you don’t have the legal right to use. If you're not sure whether you have the right to use that content, you should remove it.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}- The Roblox Team

If you believe that your content has been removed by mistake or misidentification (for example, you have authorization to use the removed content, or fair use applies) please provide us with documentation of the authorization from the party that owns the protected material so that we may review for consideration.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}How can I remove infringing content from my Roblox account?{lineBreak}{lineBreak}You can find more information on archiving assets & Experiences in the following article: https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/articles/archiving-assets-and-games{lineBreak}{lineBreak}For more information please reference the following articles:{lineBreak}{lineBreak}https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/115004647846-Roblox-Terms-of-Use {lineBreak}{lineBreak}https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/articles/Copyright-Guidance{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Admin Team{strikeDescriptor}
translation: 您好，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}連結：{contentLink}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}此內容因可能侵犯 {company} 所擁有的智慧財產權而遭到移除。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 尊重他人的智慧財產權，並對所有 Roblox 社群成員也有相同的要求。請從您的群組（包括體驗）移除您沒有權限使用的內容。您上傳他人創作的內容之前應該每次都確認您已獲得智慧財產所有者的同意。侵犯智慧財產權是違反我們的使用條款的行為，繼續使用侵權內容也可能會導致帳號停權等額外處分。如果您認為您的內容因誤會或誤判而遭到移除（例：你有權限使用被移除的內容、您的使用方式符合合理使用原則），請提供保護內容的所有者的授權文件供我們審查。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我要如何從 Roblox 帳號移除侵權內容？{lineBreak}{lineBreak}您可以在此文章了解更多關於封存素材和體驗的資訊：https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/articles/archiving-assets-and-games{lineBreak}{lineBreak}請參閱下列文章了解更多資訊：{lineBreak}{lineBreak}https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/115004647846-Roblox-Terms-of-Use {lineBreak}{lineBreak}https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/articles/Copyright-Guidance{lineBreak}{lineBreak}謝謝您，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 管理員團隊{strikeDescriptor}

description: Messaging when notifying users that an entity requested DMCA removal of their asset. (1st/2nd strike)
english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}We're reaching out to you to let you know that the following content has been removed from Roblox: {contentLink}. This content has been removed because the intellectual property owner, {company}, sent Roblox a notification telling Roblox that the content contained material that infringed their intellectual property rights. As the uploader or group owner responsible for that content, a strike was assigned to your account.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox respects the intellectual property rights of others and requires that all members of the Roblox community do the same. You should make sure you have permission from the relevant rights holder before uploading content you haven't created or allowing such content to be uploaded to a group that you own. You should remove from your account and/or group, including within your Experiences, content that belongs to others that you don’t have permission to use. Intellectual property infringement violates our Terms of Use and, if you accrue further strikes, may result in your account being terminated under our Repeat Infringer Policy.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}What can I do if I have the right to use the removed content?{lineBreak}If you believe that your content has been removed because of mistake or misidentification (for example, you have authorization to use the removed content, or fair use applies) you may contest the takedown notice by submitting a counter-notice.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Be aware that submitting a counter-notice may have serious consequences.{lineBreak}If the person who submitted the takedown notice believes that your counter-notice is not accurate, or your content is infringing, he/she may file a lawsuit against you. Likewise, submitting a knowingly false counter-notice is illegal and can subject you to liability.{lineBreak}If we determine that your counter-notice is compliant, we will forward it to the person who submitted the takedown notice. Based on a valid counter-notice, Roblox will generally restore your content within 10-14 business days, unless we are informed that a lawsuit was filed against you. To file a counter-notice you may use our customer support form https://www.roblox.com/support or you can email your counter-notice to copyright_agent@roblox.com. Please note that if you’re under 13 years old, your parent or legal guardian must submit the counter-notice on your behalf.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Please make sure that your counter-notice contains the following information:{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Link(s) to the affected content;{lineBreak}A statement under penalty of perjury that you have a good-faith belief that the content was removed/disabled as a result of a mistake or misidentification;{lineBreak}A statement that you consent to the jurisdiction of the United States federal district court for the judicial district in which your address is located (or if your address is outside of the United States, for any judicial district in which Roblox may be found) and that you will accept service of process from the person who submitted the takedown notice or their agent.{lineBreak}Your full name, postal address, and telephone number. We may forward this information to the intellectual property owner as part of your counter-notice.{lineBreak}Your electronic signature;{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Can I have the strike removed from my account?{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox will not consider a strike under our repeat infringer policy if{lineBreak}(a) the claimant who filed the takedown notice withdraws the notice; or {lineBreak}(b) you successfully challenge the takedown notice through our counter-notification process.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Is there anything else I should consider doing at this time?{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Yes. You should consider enrolling in the remediation program. If you enroll in the remediation program within 10 days of receiving this message (following the process described below) we will take that into consideration when reviewing your account for removal under our repeat infringer policy.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}How do I enroll in the remediation program?{lineBreak}Please follow these steps:{lineBreak}{lineBreak}1) Carefully read our educational materials, found at {copyrightEducationUrl}. They contain information about intellectual property rights.{lineBreak}2) Within 10 days of receiving this message, send an email to copyright_agent@roblox.com with the message “I have read the educational materials and want to enroll" and your username in the body of the email. Please note that if you’re under 13 years old, your parent or legal guardian must contact us on your behalf.{lineBreak}3) Closely review content you previously uploaded on Roblox. If you're not sure whether you have the right to use that content, please archive it. You can find more about the archiving Assets and Experiences at {archivingUrl}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}The Roblox Admin Team
translation: 您好，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我們想讓您知道以下內容已從 Roblox 移除：{contentLink}。移除的原因為智慧財產權所有者 {company} 已向 Roblox 告知該內容含有侵犯自己的智慧財產權的素材。身為該內容的上傳者或負責該內容的群組主人，您的帳號已獲得了侵權紀錄。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 尊重他人的智慧財產權，並要求所有 Roblox 社群成員給予同等的尊重。您在上傳不是自己創作的內容或允許該內容上傳到您擁有的群組時，應先確認自己獲得了相關權利所有者的同意。您應從自己的帳號、群組及體驗移除他人擁有而您沒有權限使用的內容。侵犯智慧財產權行為違反了我們的使用挑款，重複累積侵權紀錄可能會導致您的帳號根據重複侵權者政策遭到停權。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}如果我有權利使被移除的內容的話應該怎麼辦？{lineBreak}如果您認為您的內容因錯誤或誤判遭到移除（例：您已獲准使用被移除的內容，或使用方式適用公平使用原則），您可以使用回復通知挑戰下架通知。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}請注意，送出回復通知可能會有嚴重的後果。{lineBreak}如果送出下架通知的一方認為您的回復通知不準確或您的內容有侵權行為，該方可能會向您提出訴訟。同樣地，送出自知有誤的回復通知是違法行為，您可能會因此承擔責任。{lineBreak}如果我們認為您的回復通知符合規定，我們會轉給送出下架通知的一方。Roblox 根據有效的回復通知一般會在 10 到 14 個工作日之間回復您的內容，除非我們被告知您已被訴訟。若要送出回復通知，您可以使用我們的客服表單 https://www.roblox.com/support 或傳送電子郵件給 copyright_agent@roblox.com。請注意：13 歲以下的使用者必須由家長或法定監護人代表聯絡我們。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}請確認您的回復通知含有下列資訊：{lineBreak}{lineBreak}受到影響的內容的連結。{lineBreak}在偽證罪的處罰規定之下，您憑良心認為因對內容的誤會或誤判而遭到移除或停用的聲明。{lineBreak}您接受所在地址的美國聯邦地區法院轄區的管轄（如果地址不在美國，則為任何 Roblox 所在地區法院轄區），並接受送出下架通知的人或其代理人的訴訟書狀送達。{lineBreak}您的全名、郵寄地址及電話號碼。我們可以做為受理回復通知的一環而將此資訊轉給智慧財產權所有者。{lineBreak}您的電子簽名。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我的帳號的侵權紀錄可以消除嗎？{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 在以下情形不會根據重複侵權者政策認定侵權紀錄：{lineBreak}(a) 申請下架通知的一方撤回通知；或{lineBreak}(b) 您成功透過我們的回復通程序挑戰了下架通知。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我目前還可以考慮甚麼方案嗎？{lineBreak}{lineBreak}可以。您可以考慮加入我們的感化企劃。如果您在收到這則訊息的 10 天以內依照下方描述之程序加入感化企劃，我們在根據重複侵權者政策進行您的帳號的消除審查時將會考慮這點。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我要怎麼加入感化企劃？{lineBreak}請完成下列步驟：{lineBreak}{lineBreak}1) 請詳閱我們的教學內容，您可以在 {copyrightEducationUrl} 前往內容。內容中含有關於智慧財產權的資訊。{lineBreak}2) 收到這條訊息的 10 天以內傳送電子郵件到 copyright_agent@roblox.com，並在內文寫上您的使用者名稱和此訊息：「我已閱讀教學內容並想加入」。請注意：13 歲以下的使用者必須由家長或法定監護人代表聯絡我們。{lineBreak}3) 仔細審查您先前上傳到 Roblox 的內容。如果您不確定您是否有權利使用該內容，請封存該內容。您可以在 {archivingUrl} 進一步了解關於封存體驗和素材的資訊。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}謝謝您，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox 管理員團隊

description: email template (HTML) for PremiumExpiredMessage
english:
Dear {userName},

Your Roblox Premium subscription ended today

If you renew Roblox Premium , you will continue to receive benefits such as…

- Reciving your monthly Robux stipend

- Discounts when buying Robux

- Access to Premium benefits in experiences

- Access to the Trade System


Happy Gaming!

Thanks from - The Roblox Team

{userName} 您好，

您的 Roblox Premium 今天到期了

若您續訂 Roblox Premium ，您將會繼續獲得以下福利：

- 每月 Robux 津貼

- 以優惠價購買 Robux

- 使用體驗內 Premium 福利

- 使用交易系統


祝您遊戲愉快！

Roblox 團隊感謝您

Roblox now includes automatic translation support for our developers! This service is provided in the form of two quotas: an initial and a monthly. Initial quota is meant to help you get started on localizing your entire experience. Over time, as you update your experience, monthly quota will renew to ensure a continuously localized experience.

english: Engagement-Based Payouts (EBP) rewards you for making awesome experiences on Roblox that Premium subscribers love. If a Premium subscriber is visiting your experiences, you may earn an Engagement-Based Payout, even if the user isn’t spending Robux in your experiences. These payouts are on top of what you earn from selling items in your experience. You can spend your payout on Roblox or you can convert it to cash if you meet the {devexLinkStart}DevEx requirements{devexLinkEnd}.
translation: 互動度回饋（Engagement-Based Payouts，簡稱 EBP）將獎勵您在 Roblox 上創造出 Premium 訂閱者喜愛的精彩體驗。如果有 Premium 訂閱者造訪您的體驗，即使該使用者沒有在您的體驗中花費 Robux，您仍有機會獲得互動度回饋。這些回饋是除了您在體驗中販售道具所賺取的獲利之外，可獲得的額外盈利項目。您可以在 Roblox 上花費所獲得的回饋，或者在達到 {devexLinkStart}DevEx 條件{devexLinkEnd}的情況下將其兌現。

english: To see how much you’ve earned from Engagement-Based Payouts, check your {sumLinkStart}Robux history{sumLinkEnd}.
translation: 如要查看您的互動度回饋收入，請查閱您的 {sumLinkStart}Robux 紀錄{sumLinkEnd}。

description: Not used
english: Engagement-Based Payouts are calculated per experience based on your Premium Engagement Score. The Premium Engagement Score shows how popular your experience is among Premium subscribers as compared to other experiences. So if Premium subscribers are visiting your experience more than any other experience, your  Engagement-Based Payout may be higher. You can see what your Premium Engagement Score and Engagement-Based Payouts are in {devStatsLinkStart}Developer Statistics{devStatsLinkEnd}.
translation: 互動度回饋會根據每個體驗的 Premium 互動分數分開計算。Premium 互動分數可讓您知道您的體驗在 Premium 訂閱者間的人氣如何。如果 Premium 訂閱者比起其他的體驗更常來到您的體驗，那麼您也可能獲得更高的互動度回饋。您可以在{devStatsLinkStart}開發人員統計資料{devStatsLinkEnd}中看到您的 Premium 互動分數和互動度回饋。

english: To increase your Engagement-Based Payouts, you can encourage your visitors to buy Premium by building exclusive levels, items, and benefits for Premium subscribers and using the {modalLinkStart}Premium Upsell modal{modalLinkEnd} to allow them to purchase Premium in your experience.
translation: 如要提高您的互動度回饋，您可以鼓勵訪客購買 Premium，例如為 Premium 訂閱者打造專屬關卡、道具和福利，並使用 {modalLinkStart}Premium 追加銷售視窗{modalLinkEnd}讓他們能在您的體驗中直接購買 Premium。

english: To benefit from Engagement-Based Payouts, your experience must be free to access.

You can see what your Premium engagement score and Premium Payouts are in {devStatsLinkStart}Developer Statistics{devStatsLinkEnd}

english: You must wait {promotionTermNum} days from the time of purchase before canceling your promotional Roblox Premium Builders Club membership. You can then cancel the membership at any time after {promotionTermNum} days. You must cancel before the next renewal date to stop a recurring charge. You will still receive the full time you have previously paid for.
translation: 您只能在購買 {promotionTermNum} 天後取消您的促銷 Roblox Premium Builders Club 會員資格。過了 {promotionTermNum} 天以後，您就可以隨時取消。若要停止定期收費，您必須在續訂日期取消會員資格。您先前付費所獲得的天數不會受到影響。

english: Your Roblox Premium membership cannot be canceled at this time as it is currently in the process of renewal with our payment processor, which briefly disallows changes to the membership during this time. Once the renewal process is complete, the membership can be canceled and you will still receive the full amount of time paid for. For further information, please contact {linkStart}Customer Service{linkEnd}. Please note, Customer Service is unable to cancel a membership until the renewal process is complete.
translation: 您的 Roblox Premium 會員資格目前正在透過付款服務續訂，目前無法取消。您在付款服務處理會員資格時無法做出任何變更。您可以在續訂過程完成後取消會員資格，並保留您付費所獲得的天數。若要取得更多資訊，請聯絡{linkStart}客服人員{linkEnd}。請注意，客服人員無法在續訂過程完成之前取消會員資格。

english: How do I get a Roblox promotional code?
translation: 我要如何取得 Roblox 促銷序號？

english: You may receive a Roblox promo code from one of our many events or giveaways. Valid codes will earn you a virtual good that will be added to your Roblox account.
translation: 您可以在 Roblox 活動或大放送獲得促銷序號。兌換有效的促銷序號後，您的 Roblox 帳號將會收到一個虛擬商品。

english: How do I use my promotional code?
translation: 我要如何使用 Roblox 促銷序號？

english: This is the place to claim your goods. Enter the promo code in the section to the right and your free virtual good will be automatically added to your Roblox account. Remember that promo codes may expire or only be active for a short period of time, so make sure to use your code right away.
translation: 您可以在這裡領取商品。在右方輸入促銷序號後，免費的虛擬商品將會自動加到您的 Roblox 帳號。促銷序號有可能有限定的兌換期間，也有可能會過期，拿到促銷序號之後請盡快兌換。

description: Moderator note shown to user when serving consequence
english: Roblox does not permit real threats of violence towards members of the Roblox Community.
translation: Roblox 不允許對 Roblox 社群成員的真實暴力威脅。

english: Roblox does not permit associations with terrorism or violent extremism.
translation: Roblox 不允許與恐怖主義或暴力極端主義有所關連。

english: Roblox does not permit the encouragement of or participation in real-life dangerous activities among community members
translation: Roblox 不允許社群成員之間鼓勵參與或直接參與危險的現實生活行為。

english: Roblox does not permit the exchange of Personal Identifiable Information (PII) between community members.
translation: Roblox 不允許社群成員之間交換 PII（Personally identifiable information ，個人可識別資訊）。

english: Roblox does not permit bullying or harassment towards community members.
translation: Roblox 不允許霸凌或騷擾社群成員。

english: Roblox does not permit discriminatory language, behavior, or content of any kind.
translation: Roblox 不允許任何形式的歧視性言論、行為或內容。

english: Roblox does not permit sexual content in any form on the platform.
translation: Roblox 不允許平台上任何形式的色情內容。

english: Roblox does not permit violent content and gore, including excessive use of blood in images or videos.
translation: Roblox 不允許暴力和血腥內容，包括在圖像或影片中過度使用血。

english: Roblox does not permit illegal or regulated content in any form. This can include alcohol, drugs, tobacco products, or bomb or weapon making.
translation: Roblox 不允許任何形式的違法或管制內容，這其中包括酒精、毒品、菸草產品、炸彈製作及武器製作。

english: Roblox does not permit dating or romantic exchanges between avatars.
translation: Roblox 不允許虛擬人偶之間的約會或浪漫交流。

english: Roblox does not permit profane language or slurs.
Roblox does not permit support for current political candidates, parties, associated flags or symbols.
translation: Roblox 不允許對現前政黨、候選人及相關旗幟、標誌等的聲援。

english: Roblox does not permit phishing or scamming links, requests for passwords, selling of accounts, uploading of unauthorized accounts, selling Roblox assets for real money off platform, or artificially inflating numbers associated with experiences.
translation: Roblox 不允許釣魚或詐騙連結、請求密碼、販售帳號、上傳未經許可的帳號、在平台外販售 Roblox 資產獲得真錢或人為膨脹體驗相關數據。

english: Roblox does not permit spamming in the form of clickbait, or repetitive, large volume messaging.
translation: Roblox 不允許騙點、重複洗版等垃圾內容。

english: Roblox does not permit users to mislead others by impersonating other people’s real- or virtual-world identity or affiliations.
translation: Roblox 不允許使用者假冒別人的真實或虛擬身分或關係而誤導他人。

english: Roblox does not permit the use of off-site links of any kind. Links to Guilded, YouTube, Facebook, Discord, Twitter, and Twitch must be wrapped in the applicable Policy API or listed in the Social Networks and Social Links settings of your profile or experience description page. Links that appear in locations where the API cannot be deployed - such as text chat - are prohibited.
translation: Roblox 不允許任何形式的站外連結。Guilded、YouTube、Facebook、Discord、Twitter 及 Twitch 連結必須包覆在對應的政策 API 之中，或在個人檔案或體驗說明頁面的社交網路及社交連結設定中列出。連結禁止在文字聊天等無法部署 API 的場所中出現。

english: Roblox does not permit attempts to threaten users in order to force them to do something they do not want to do.
translation: Roblox 不允許威脅其他使用者，強迫他做出自己不想做的事情。

english: Roblox does not permit uploads of audio that is unintelligible, excessively loud, screaming, or high-pitched noises.
translation: Roblox 不允許上傳擁有下列性質的音訊：無法辨識、音量過大、大叫、聲音尖銳。

english: Roblox does not permit users to deploy or discuss any method of cheating on platform.
translation: Roblox 不允許使用者在平台上部署或討論任何形式的作弊手段。

english: Roblox does not permit bypasses of our systems that keep our platform and community safe and secure.
translation: Roblox 不允許繞過維護平台和社群安全的系統。

english: Roblox does not permit using third-parties to buy, sell, or trade Robux, promotional codes that falsely appear to be from Roblox Corporation, or inappropriate use of the group payout system.
translation: Roblox 不允許使用第三方服務購買、販售或交易 Robux 或看似來自 Roblox Corporation 的促銷序號，亦不允許不當使用群組支出系統。

english: Roblox does not permit content that recreates, mocks, or capitalizes off of specific real-world tragic events.
translation: Roblox 不允許重現、輕視或利用特定真實災難事件的內容。

english: Roblox does not permit users to violate intellectual property rights.
translation: Roblox 不允許使用者違反智慧財產權。

english: Roblox does not allow this type of advertisement. Please ensure your ad content complies with the Roblox Advertising Standards.

translation: Premium 遊戲時間分數將每天根據 Roblox Premium 玩家在您的遊戲所花的時間計算。

賺取的 Premium 遊戲時間 Robux

english: We're currently experiencing delays. Please check again later.

english: The selected date range includes periods ineligible for Premium Payouts.
translation: 選擇的日期範圍含有不符合 Premium 支付資格的日期。
歡迎來到 Premium 支付！

english: Premium Payouts rewards you for making awesome games on Roblox that Premium subscribers love. If a Premium subscriber is playing your games, you’re earning a Premium payout, even if the user isn’t spending Robux in your games. These payouts are on top of what you earn from selling items in game. You can spend your payout on Roblox or you can convert it to cash if you meet the {devexLinkStart}DevEx requirements{devexLinkEnd}.
translation: 如果您的遊戲常常有 Premium 會員來玩，您就可以透過 Premium 支付賺取 Robux！只要 Premium 會員在您的遊戲裡，不管他有沒有花 Robux，您一樣會獲得 Premium 支付金額。Premium 支付金額可以與您在遊戲中販賣道具的收入重疊。您獲得的 Robux 可以直接在 Roblox 裡使用，符合 {devexLinkStart}DevEx 資格{devexLinkEnd}的創作者也可以將 Robux 轉換為現金。

english: To see how much you’ve earned from Premium Payouts, check your {sumLinkStart}Robux history{sumLinkEnd}.
translation: 若要查看您從 Premium 支付獲得的 Robux，請前往您的 {sumLinkStart}Robux 紀錄{sumLinkEnd}。

english: To increase your Premium Payouts, you can encourage your visitors to buy Premium by building exclusive levels, items, and benefits for Premium subscribers and using the {modalLinkStart}Premium Upsell modal{modalLinkEnd} to allow them to purchase Premium in your experience.
translation: 若要增加您的 Premium 支付金額，您可以創作 Premium 訪客限定的等級、道具及福利，並且在遊戲內對玩家{modalLinkStart}追加銷售 Premium{modalLinkEnd}。

english: To benefit from Premium Payouts, your experience must be a free experience.
translation: 只有免費體驗才可以獲得 Premium 支付金額。
{moreInfoLinkStart}前往此處了解更多關於 Premium 支付的資訊{moreInfoLinkEnd}。

english: See how many universe visits are from Premium subscribers.
translation: 看看來自 Premium 訂閱者的宇宙造訪次數有多少。

english: Premium visits are measured every hour by how many visits are ended by a Premium subscriber.
translation: Premium 造訪次數會每個小時統計 Premium 訂閱者造訪您的遊戲的次數。

english: Premium visit percentage shows you what proportion of your total visits are from Premium subscribers.
translation: Premium 造訪比例會告訴您 Premium 訂閱者佔您的總造訪次數的比例。

english: Increasing Premium visits helps increase your engagement score, which increases your Premium Payout.
translation: 高的 Premium 造訪次數有助於提高互動分數，Premium 支付金額也會更多。

english: Increase {startLink}Roblox Premium{endLink} users' playtime in your experience to earn payouts. {learnLinkStart}Learn more{learnLinkEnd}.
translation: 只要 {startLink}Roblox Premium{endLink} 使用者在您的體驗花更多時間，您就可以獲得支付金額。前往{learnLinkStart}此處{learnLinkEnd}了解更多。

english: See how often the Premium prompt is shown in your experience and how often a visitor buys Premium from it.
translation: 看看 Premium 視窗在您的體驗顯示的頻率和訪客透過視窗購買 Premium 的頻率。

english: Conversions are how many times a visitor buys Premium from your Premium upsell.
translation: 轉換數為訪客透過 Premium 追加銷售訊息購買 Premium 的次數。

english: Increasing your conversion helps increase your engagement score, which increases your Premium Payout.
translation: 高的轉換數有助於提高互動分數，Premium 支付金額也會更多。

english: Conversion rate is calculated as the proportion of conversions to impressions (# of conversions / # of impressions).
translation: 轉換率為轉換數與曝光數的比率（轉換數 / 曝光數）。

english: Impressions are how many times your Premium upsell is shown.
translation: 曝光數為 Premium 追加銷售訊息顯示的次數。

english: Premium Payouts are calculated per experience based on your Premium playtime score. The Premium playtime score shows how popular your experience is among Premium subscribers as compared to other experiences. So if Premium subscribers are playing your experience more than any other experience, your Premium Payout will be higher! You can see what your Premium playtime score and Premium Payouts are in the {devStatsLinkStart}Premium Payouts chart{devStatsLinkEnd} in Developer Statistics.
translation: Premium 支付金額會根據您每一個體驗的 Premium 體驗時間分數而分開計算。Premium 體驗時間分數會讓您知道您的體驗在 Premium 會員間的相對人氣。如果 Premium 會員在您的體驗的時間比在其他體驗的時間多，您也會獲得更多 Premium 支付金額！您可以在開發者數據中的{devStatsLinkStart}Premium 支付圖表{devStatsLinkEnd}看到您的 Premium 體驗時間分數和 Premium 支付金額。

english: You don't qualify for Premium Payouts because you have a paid access game
translation: 您擁有付費遊戲，不符合 Premium 支付資格

english: Generate and download .CSV files of your experiences's sales data. Each file contains a month's worth of data broken down by the item sold and the place it was sold in. english: Below are some top level metrics that can be used to help analyze game performance. Information here can be filtered by date range. Every new datapoint is added during a 24-hour period.
translation: 以下是一些可以協助分析遊戲效能的頂層指標。以下的資訊可以依照日期範圍篩選。每 24 小時將會新增一個資料點。

english: Below are some metrics related to acquiring new users and the number of active users you have for your game. Information here can be filtered by date range. Every new datapoint is added during a 24-hour period.
translation: 以下是一些與獲得新使用者和遊戲活躍使用者數相關的指標。以下的資訊可以依照日期範圍篩選。每 24 小時將會新增一個資料點。

english: Number of hours played over the selected time period.
The number of total plays or visits you receive in a day (DAU) or month (MAU). This includes the same user playing your game in different sessions.
translation: 您單日（DAU）或單月（MAU）獲得的總參訪次數，包括多次玩您的遊戲的單一使用者。

english: Below are some metrics related to retention to help you understand how to gain new recurring users as well as continue to engage them. Information here can be filtered by date range. Every new datapoint is added during a 24-hour period.
translation: 以下是一些幫助您了解您獲得新使用者和持續與他們互動的能力的的保留率指標。以下的資訊可以依照日期範圍篩選。每 24 小時將會新增一個資料點。

english: ***Note that all data points are updated at 08:00:00.000Z in UTC. This means that if you are in a time zone west of UTC, such as Pacific Time, there can be perceived delays for when data is updated for the next day. Likewise, if you are based in a time zone east of UTC, it may appear that data is being updated at an earlier time. This is because the date filter at the top adjusts to your local time zone but the data points shown below are all in UTC.
translation: *** 注意：所有資料點會在世界協調時間 08:00:00.000Z 更新。如果您所在的時區位於世界協調時區西方（例：太平洋時間），隔日的資料更新看起來會延後執行。同樣地，如果您所在的時區位於世界協調時區東方，隔日的資料更新看起來會提早執行。此情形地原因為上方的日期篩選會依您的時區調整，但以下資料點皆以世界協調時間為準。

english: By clicking “Activate”, you consent to allow the data of your users to be shared with external data services for the sole purpose of analytics. Your users’ data will only be used for calculating aggregated analytics for each experience. Roblox is not responsible for the data handling  practices of these third parties, so you will want to preview their privacy policy for more information.
translation: 您點擊「啟用」即表示您同意您的使用者的資料只為了數據用途分享給外部資料服務。使用者資料只會用來計算每個體驗的整合數據。Roblox 不為第三方服務的資料處理手段負責；若您需要更多資訊，請查看該服務的隱私權政策。

english: Note: For group owned experiences, the group owner needs to turn on the “View group experience analytics” in the group role settings to allow others members to view the dashboard.
translation: 注意：若體驗為群組所擁有，群組主人必須在群組身分設定中開啟「查看群組體驗數據」才可讓其他成員查看後台。

english: By clicking “Agree,” you are agreeing to allow group editors to run queries for your experience. This will allow you to collaborate and create custom queries.
translation: 按下「同意」即表示您同意允許群組編輯者對體驗執行查詢，您們將可以合作並建立自訂查詢。

english: Note: PlayFab is a third party service provider with their own terms and privacy policies. Roblox does not control your use of their services. In order to collaborate with your group editors, you will need to provide collaborators with admin access in PlayFab.
translation: 注意：PlayFab 是第三方服務供應商，它擁有自己的條款和隱私權政策。Roblox 無法管制您對該服務的使用。若要和群組編輯者合作，您必須授予合夥人 PlayFab 的管理員權限。

description: Text for the "Run custom queries on PlayFab" button on each game's Analytics Overview page.
translation: 使用 PlayFab 執行自訂查詢

english: Congrats! Your experience has been registered in PlayFab. Experience events will now be logged and your dashboards will begin to populate in 24-48 hours.
translation: 恭喜，您的體驗已在 PlayFab 登記！體驗內活動將會被記錄，您的後台也會在 24 到 48 小時候開始出現資料。

english: You can now access your experience in PlayFab and run custom queries. Check your inbox for a PlayFab account activation email.
translation: 您已可在 PlayFab 存取體驗並執行自訂查詢，PlayFab 帳號啟用電子郵件已傳到您的收件箱。

english: Updated quarterly, benchmarks allow you to compare your game’s performance to others with similar rankings so you can set reasonable goals to get to the next tier.
translation: 您可以使用每季更新一次的指標比較您的遊戲和其他階級相似的遊戲之間的表現，讓您可以訂定合理的目標前往下一個階級。
